title: Metronome  - A Good Omens animatic

comment: Seeing Crowley’s perspective then Aziraphale’s ughh that really did it for me.
"In a life after this, we'll meet again" my heart breaks each time I replay that 😭

You know that feeling when someone predicts something in an eerily accurate way? That's what those Russian spies must have felt when Crowley tried to save Aziraphale. What a horrible way to feel before you die but they deserved it. They tried to kill Crowley's bae smh.
